:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm71.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=45.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://web1.noment.com/dsummers//EQ/Kulanae6.gif height=158 width=119></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Fear FCFS rules...what are they please</span><hr size=1> I think you missed a rather important part of Jara's message:<br><br>&quot;after another raid finishes&quot;<br><br>No one but the people invited to your raid should be in the plane during your scheduled raid time.<br><br>*edit*<br><br>In addition:<br><br>&quot;I had thought we had a more &quot;honorable&quot; system for sharing.&quot;<br><br>So you'd rather have a bunch of guilds reserving Fear just for Epic spawns and wasting other peoples opportunities for armor?  It's easy to cast blame on a system.....how about you propose an alternative approach that is fair to everyone. <p><font size=2 face="Tempus Sans ITC, Verdana, Helvetica">Kulanae Soulsease</font><br><font size=2 face="Helvetica">Virtuoso of <a href=http://www.watchers-brell.com>Watchers</a><br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8687>Profile</a><br><br><i>Joy is in the ears that hear!</i></font></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukulanaesoulsease.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kulanae Soulsease</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 3/4/02 9:51:54 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#464446><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utwiggietymberwolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twiggie Tymberwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#FFFF66>Board Moderator</font><br><font color=#A0B0E0>&#60;Silent Redemption&#62;</font></span><br>  Posts: 2820<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/4/02 10:56:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellseri